metadata.name: Auroras
metadata.description:
Morning and Evening Auroras, sisters guarding the gates to the palace of the Sun. The key they hold gives the Sun the only way to ascend to the firmament of the sky. 
Morning Aurora bears the sign of a golden boat and a silver oar with which she travels across the sky. Evening Aurora wears the constellation of a small polar bear star, which helps her always keep on the right path. 
Without them there is no Sun.
